reviewText:
after 2 years i did not play this game (played only 1 or 2 months with a friend of mine) and without using any exploits or something like that (if there are any?) i wanted to play again just for fun. but as i started the launcher it said my account has been permanently closed because i violated the terms of use?!
if inactivity counts as violation then your terms of use are violating my rights as human! (i was online with my steam acc the whole time but just did not log in into the game)


do never spend money on this piece of crap!
